{"tid":2257508,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 12 機背磁鐵   證實干擾機械錶機芯準確度","createTime":"2020-10-25T08:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T11:05:53.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"04ea0638b88e8d21a44dbf0250130a27080fb703","tid":2257508,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:12:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/10/25/iphone-12-magnet-mechinic-watch/mobile-phone/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F10%2F25%2Fiphone-12-magnet-mechinic-watch%2Fmobile-phone%2F%3F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PaxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=97305a82\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/10/25/iphone-12-magnet-mechinic-watch/mobile-phone/?</a><br />\n<br />\niPhone 12 的機背內置磁吸式無線充電線圈，內裡包含了磁鐵，可以吸附 MagSafe 充電器和保護套。中國網民 @芯隨表動日前進行了測試，發現 iPhone 12 的磁鐵會干擾部份機械手錶機芯，雖然不會造成永久損壞，但就會令手錶變得走時。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=999870\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F%3Fattachment_id%3D999870&h=d13767f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n@芯隨表動量度了 iPhone 12 Pro、MagSafe 手機殼和充電器的磁力值，分別為 57 至 60 高斯、16 高斯和 123 高斯。假如用戶右手手執 iPhone 12 Pro，機械手錶戴在左手，手錶不會受到干擾。一旦 iPhone 12 Pro 或 MagSafe 配件接觸到手錶，機芯就有機會出現誤差。<br />\n@芯隨表動測試過多款機械機芯，Omega、IWC、Breitling、Tudor 等 ETA 機芯會受到明顯影響；而 Rolex、Patek Philippe、Blancpain 和 Tudor 自家開發的機芯 則不受影響。@芯隨表動以 Omega 2500 同軸蝶飛機芯作例子，指接觸 iPhone 12 Pro 或 MagSafe 配件後，原本每日誤差 1 秒會變成每天 50 秒，除非將手錶拿去消磁才能解決。<br />\n來源：cnbeta"},{"pid":"5c43ddc9484bd123419d58eb6cc541e19b36fbe5","tid":2257508,"uid":239086,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:13:19.000Z","msg":"有啲錶有事但有啲又無影響，即係錶廠問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be46be5ad0ded903517c5eb78eb633cac31958d4","tid":2257508,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"無鬼聊<br />\n你會唔會拎粒攝石攝住隻錶"},{"pid":"473acab9b5a82057e52d2a57670cf2987ecdee2